Content:





Let's get started! :elephant:
The next sections will give you a 
[link: quick_tour.md] short tour of Nushell by example
 (including how to get help from within Nushell) and show you how to 
[link: moving_around.md] move around your file system
.
Then, because Nushell takes some design decisions that are quite different from typical shells or dynamic scripting languages, make sure to check out 
[link: thinking_in_nu.md] Thinking in Nu
 where we explain some of these concepts.
